title: Cung Danh
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An open-air cafe with a spacious plant-filled terrace, which itself sits one meter above the moat that surrounded the ancient walled fortress. Most customers come here for drinks. Offers 2 extensive, separate menus: one vegetarian (no mock meats) and the other conventional (with meat). Food is cooked to order. No English spoken. An English-language menu is sometimes available but is often misplaced. Has Wi-Fi.
